Subject: Please add “Asia Pacific (Seoul) ap-northeast-2” region to S3 Bucket Region
Description: Please add “Asia Pacific (Seoul) ap-northeast-2” region to S3 Bucket Region. KISA (Korea Internet & Security Agency), a Korean government agency, strongly recommends that customers use a domestic region for all clouds, and AWS uses the “Asia Pacific (Seoul) ap-northeast-2” region, which they have defined as a must for financial institutions such as banks, insurance companies, and exchanges.
